This PR supports `unique`, `unique0` and `priority` constructs for case operation (See SV spec 12.5.3 for more detail). 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19691120/163708537-42ac08d1-b50b-442b-a347-9e3f95be16a7.png)

Example: 
```mlir
hw.module @Foo(%cond: i1) {
  %fd = hw.constant 0 : i32
  sv.initial {
     sv.case %cond : i1 {validationQualifier = #sv<"validation_qualifier priority">}
     default: {
       sv.fwrite %fd, "zero"
   }
  }
  hw.output
 }
```
```verilog
module Foo(
  input cond);

  initial begin
    priority case (cond)
      default:
        $fwrite(32'h0, "zero");
    endcase
  end // initial
endmodule
```
Close https://github.com/llvm/circt/issues/2907
